N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 21 ยง 1275.10 - Interference, tampering or unauthorized starting of aircraft prohibited

State Regulations

No person shall interfere or tamper with any aircraft at
the air terminal, or start the engine of such aircraft without the operator's
consent. Notes
